name: Tarrant County Public Health
tweet: Flu viruses spread by tiny droplets made when people with flu cough, sneeze or talk, so be sure to cover your mouth. If you are uninsured, @tcphtweets is offering free flu shots at @Albertsons, @tomthumb_stores and @kroger. Check our list for participating stores.

name: Tarrant County Public Health
tweet: Can a flu shot give you flu? No, the flu vaccines given with a flu shot are made with either inactivated (killed) viruses, or with only a single protein from the flu virus. The nasal spray vaccine contains live viruses that are weakened so that they will not cause illness.

name: Tarrant County Public Health
tweet: #Flu vaccinations have been shown to reduce severity of illness in those people who get vaccinated but still get sick. @TCPHtweets has partnered with @albertsons, @tomthumb_stores and @kroger to provide free flu shots to the uninsured. Check our list for participating stores.
